{
  "name": "Spirit Link",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/death/undead-ghosts-trio-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>Make a Spell Check against the Repeated Charisma Save of 2 creatures within range that don’t share their HP.</p><p><strong>Check Success:</strong> If both target’s fail the Save, they are Linked for the Duration.</p><p><em><strong>DC Tip:</strong> A creature can choose to fail a Save if it want.</em></p><p><strong>Linked:</strong> While within 10 Spaces of each other, whenever one Linked creature regains or loses HP, the amount is shared with the other Linked creature.</p><p><em><strong>Example:</strong> You target yourself and an enemy, they fail the Save and you choose to fail the Save making you Linked to each other. When the enemy drinks a healing potion to heal 2 HP, you instead heal for 1 HP each, splitting the healing between you.</em></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Apply Spirit Link to one token. Another will be added by the effect macro. Effect will not be removed automatically.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Extended Link: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The maximum range of the Link increases by 5 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Lion’s Heart: (1 MP)</strong> While within range of the link, each target gains Resistance to Charmed, Taunted, Intimidated, Frightened, and Terrified).</p><p><strong>Transference: (3 MP)</strong> Instead of sharing HP regained or lost while Linked, choose 1 target to receive all the changes in HP.</p><p><strong>Profane: (3 MP)</strong> Instead of sharing loses of HP while Linked, both creatures lose the full amount of HP.</p><p></p>",
